OL,3,C'Worst war I've seen': Strikes
OL,4,Ccontinue in southern Lebanon ahead of
OL,5,Cpeace talks
OL,7,FCorrespondent John Ray reports from
OL,8,FTyre, southern Lebanon, ahead of the
OL,9,Ffirst round of direct diplomatic talks
OL,10,Fbetween Lebanon and Israel
OL,12,FFrom our viewpoint by the coast, I am
OL,13,Fwatching Israeli missiles explode on
OL,14,Fprecisely the same stretch of southern
OL,15,FLebanon ` the same villages and
OL,16,Fhillsides ` where their bombs landed
OL,17,Fthe last time I was here in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
