FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776269466
OL,3,C'Worst war I've seen': Strikes
OL,4,Ccontinue in southern Lebanon ahead of
OL,5,Cpeace talks
OL,7,FThere is the familiar roar of Israeli
OL,8,Fjets and then, unusually, a loud blast
OL,9,Foverhead. We're told it's a failed
OL,10,Fattempt to bring down the Israeli
OL,11,Fdrone that's been circling for some
OL,12,Ftime.
OL,14,FMore than once over the past two
OL,15,Fyears, Israel's Prime Minister
OL,16,FBinjamin Netanyahu has boasted of
OL,17,FHezbollah's defeat. But clearly, there
OL,18,Fis still more fighting to be done.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776269466
OL,3,C'Worst war I've seen': Strikes
OL,4,Ccontinue in southern Lebanon ahead of
OL,5,Cpeace talks
OL,7,FIt is one of the reasons hopes have
OL,8,Fbeen so low ahead of today's rare,
OL,9,Fface-to-face meeting between Israeli
OL,10,Fand Lebanese government officials in
OL,11,FWashington.
OL,13,FThe other reason for pessimism is the
OL,14,Fprior rejection of the talks by
OL,15,FHezbollah. The Lebanese government is
OL,16,Fin no position to force the Iranian-
OL,17,Fbacked militia to submit, no more than
OL,18,Fthe Israeli army, it would seem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
