PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776269466
OL,3,C'Worst war I've seen': Strikes
OL,4,Ccontinue in southern Lebanon ahead of
OL,5,Cpeace talks
OL,7,FThe yellow and green flags tell us we
OL,8,Fare in Hezbollah country ` so too do
OL,9,Fthe large portraits of Iranian
OL,10,Fleaders; Hezbollah's sponsors for four
OL,11,Fdecades.
OL,13,FThis has been called a war within a
OL,14,Fwar ` though it is just as lethal as
OL,15,Fthe conflict across the Gulf, with the
OL,16,Fdeath toll topping 2,000.
OL,18,FMore than a million people have fled
OL,19,Ftheir homes. Others have sought some
OL,20,Fsafety here, in Tyre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
