FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776269466
OL,3,C'Worst war I've seen': Strikes
OL,4,Ccontinue in southern Lebanon ahead of
OL,5,Cpeace talks
OL,7,FThe usually bustling streets are
OL,8,Fdeadly quiet. Those who've stayed do
OL,9,Fso because they fear they will never
OL,10,Fbe allowed to return home.
OL,12,FIsrael says it wants to occupy a broad
OL,13,Fswathe of territory in the south, to
OL,14,Fguarantee the security of its own
OL,15,Fborder from Hezbollah attack.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
