OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776269466
OL,3,C'Worst war I've seen': Strikes
OL,4,Ccontinue in southern Lebanon ahead of
OL,5,Cpeace talks
OL,7,FIn his 70 years, Abdel Rahman has seen
OL,8,Fmany Israeli-Lebanese conflicts. But
OL,9,Fhe's never before watched his friends
OL,10,Fand neighbours killed in front of his
OL,11,Feyes.
OL,13,FAn airstrike hit their apartment
OL,14,Fbuilding just as he returned home. He
OL,15,Fcounts it as a miracle that he
OL,16,Fsurvived.
OL,18,FWe find him sitting forlornly on the
OL,19,Fcorner of the street, a few metres
OL,20,Ffrom the piles of blasted concrete.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776269466
OL,3,C'Worst war I've seen': Strikes
OL,4,Ccontinue in southern Lebanon ahead of
OL,5,Cpeace talks
OL,7,F"This is the worst war I have seen,"
OL,8,Fhe tells me.
OL,10,FI ask if he has any hope for peace.
OL,12,F"Only when the Israelis stop," he
OL,13,Freplies.
OL,15,FI say the Israelis might stop if
OL,16,FHezbollah also stopped. This latest
OL,17,Fround of fighting back after Hezbollah
OL,18,Frockets targeted Israel in retaliation
OL,19,Ffor the killing of Ayatollah Khamenei.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
